ml_tags: Annie Ann Cecilia Waterhouse 12.2.1955 - 25.6.2022 Grandma to Harrison & Georgia Adored Mother to Warren & Noni Sister to Kate, John, Peter, Liz & Warren Teacher & friend to all Her early leaf's a flower; But only so an hour. Nature's first green is gold, Her hardest hue to hold. Then leaf subsides to leaf, So Eden sank to grief. So dawn goes down to day, Nothing gold can stay.
